<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="405" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[140,1346,2542,3481]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[142,490,3329,3362]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Tibetan Shrew is distributed at high elevations without anthropogenic activities. Its population presumably is not declining.
</paragraph>
